  <heading>REV32</heading>
  <desc>
    <brief>
      <para>Reverse bytes in 32-bit words</para>
    </brief>
    <authored>
      <para>This instruction reverses the byte order in each 32-bit
word of a register.</para>
    </authored>
  </desc>
